## **Non-Functional Requirements**

### **Performance**

* \[\] **Page Load Times**: All pages load within 2 seconds on standard broadband (3G+)  
* \[\] **AI Processing**: Synthesis generation completes within 10 seconds (user never waits \>15 seconds)  
* \[\] **PDF Generation**: Downloads initiate within 3 seconds of button click  
* \[\] **Real-Time Updates**: Tier upgrades reflect immediately in UI (no manual refresh required)  
* \[\] **Mobile Performance**: Touch interactions respond within 100ms, scrolling is smooth (60fps)

### **Scalability**

* \[\] **User Concurrency**: System handles 1,000+ simultaneous users without performance degradation  
* \[\] **Referral Tracking**: Database efficiently handles referral relationships for 100,000+ users (indexed queries)  
* \[\] **File Storage**: PDF reports stored efficiently (cache identical reports, avoid duplicate generation)  
* \[\] **API Rate Limiting**: AI synthesis endpoints rate-limited to prevent abuse (e.g., max 10 generations per user per hour)

### **Security**

* \[\] **Authentication**: Secure session management via Supabase Auth (JWT tokens, httpOnly cookies)  
* \[\] **Data Privacy**: User data encrypted at rest (Supabase default) and in transit (HTTPS)  
* \[\] **Access Control**: Tier-based permissions enforced at backend (not just UI hiding)  
* \[\] **Referral Link Security**: Unique codes generated with sufficient entropy (UUID or similar, no predictable patterns)  
* \[\] **PDF Security**: Reports only accessible to authenticated users who own the data (signed URLs or access-controlled storage)

### **Accessibility**

* \[\] **WCAG 2.1 AA Compliance**: Color contrast ratios meet standards (4.5:1 for body text, 3:1 for large text)  
* \[\] **Keyboard Navigation**: All interactive elements accessible via keyboard (Tab, Enter, Esc)  
* \[\] **Screen Reader Support**: All modals, forms, buttons properly labeled with ARIA attributes  
* \[\] **Focus Management**: Focus trapped in modals, clear focus indicators (visible outlines)  
* \[\] **Error Messaging**: Clear, descriptive error messages for form validation (not just "error occurred")  
* \[\] **Responsive Design**: Usable on devices from 320px (mobile) to 1920px+ (desktop)

